  • public class QueryResultJson
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by btesila on 5/22/2014. This class is used in order to map the sync server response to an object. Since the server gives a complex response, the QueryResultJson object makes use of other objects in order to map all the corresponding attributes accordingly.
